if there's a problem?

738
00:48:18,660 --> 00:48:19,740
The color.

739
00:48:20,340 --> 00:48:22,660
The wound will turn dark red.

740
00:48:29,300 --> 00:48:31,100
Wait here until the results are out.

741
00:48:34,420 --> 00:48:35,620
