This should be enough for you to move.

743
00:48:57,660 --> 00:48:59,020
Tell me if you get thirsty.

744
00:49:00,100 --> 00:49:01,700
Ms. Yoon, step out for a minute.

745
00:49:07,620 --> 00:49:08,740
I told you, didn't I?

746
00:49:09,380 --> 00:49:10,540
You'll be fine.

747
00:49:11,420 --> 00:49:12,860
