761
00:51:13,280 --> 00:51:16,320
If you get bitten,
you'll get infected no matter what.

762
00:51:18,160 --> 00:51:19,920
Your condition gets worse

763
00:51:20,000 --> 00:51:21,600
and your time
as a normal person decreases.

764
00:51:23,160 --> 00:51:25,880
You never know
when you'll get thirsty and attack others.

765
00:51:25,960 --> 00:51:27,720
So it's only natural
that visits are restricted.

766
00:51:30,280 --> 00:51:31,600
Is there a way to treat it?

767
00:51:34,760 --> 00:51:36,120
None at the moment.

768
00:51:37,680 --> 00:51:39,640
If it gets worse,
you'll always feel thirsty.

769
00:51:40,280 --> 00:51:42,520
You lose reason and attack anyone you see.

770
00:51:44,320 --> 00:51:46,000
The only thing we can do right now

771
00:51:46,080 --> 00:51:48,360
is to slow down that process.

772
00:51:52,240 --> 00:51:54,920
So it's true nobody made it out alive.

773
00:51:59,200 --> 00:52:00,480
Ms. Yoon,

774
00:52:01,200 --> 00:52:02,720
