This is

807
00:57:50,140 --> 00:57:51,500
a huge scoop.

808
00:58:32,860 --> 00:58:34,940
(Seyang Dream Car Wash)

809
00:58:37,580 --> 00:58:39,220
Why not go in if he's in there?

810
00:58:39,660 --> 00:58:41,540
I'm waiting for someone.

811
00:58:41,620 --> 00:58:43,540
Who? Did you call for backup?

812
00:58:44,140 --> 00:58:45,260
Speak of the devil.

813
00:58:47,260 --> 00:58:49,820
What? My goodness.

814
00:58:50,180 --> 00:58:52,140
Lieutenant Colonel Han Tae-seok.

815
00:58:52,500 --> 00:58:53,860
What brings you here?

816
00:58:53,940 --> 00:58:54,940
The dealer.

817
00:58:55,420 --> 00:58:57,940
Senior Officer Jung
and I will go meet him. Do you mind?

818
00:58:58,700 --> 00:59:02,180
No, not at all. I'll just wait here.

819
00:59:09,500 --> 00:59:10,860
-Hey--
-I know.

820
00:59:10,940 --> 00:59:12,180
Stand guard.

821
00:59:14,260 --> 00:59:15,900
I really can't stand him.

822
00:59:16,460 --> 00:59:18,300
Why are you really here?

823
00:59:19,100 --> 00:59:21,820
Next's manufacturer had the rest
of the supply stored in their warehouse.

824
00:59:21,900 --> 00:59:23,700
I want to find out who released it.

825
00:59:23,940 --> 00:59:27,540
I saw the news. It looks like this disease
has spread to other countries.

826
00:59:27,820 --> 00:59:29,380
Was Next sold worldwide?

827
00:59:30,380 --> 00:59:31,900
I told you I had a knack for stealing

828
00:59:32,580 --> 00:59:34,580
although I was never good
at making things.

829
00:59:36,420 --> 00:59:37,900
I stole it for a foreign company.

830
00:59:38,300 --> 00:59:39,660
Back in my Competitive Advantage days.

831
00:59:43,460 --> 00:59:44,780
He's really something.

832
01:00:00,580 --> 01:00:01,580
There are three of them.

833
01:00:02,460 --> 01:00:03,780
Hey, turn off the lights!

834
01:00:08,580 --> 01:00:09,860
(Exit)

835
01:00:09,860 --> 01:00:11,100
(Exit)
Did you bring the rest?

836
01:00:11,100 --> 01:00:11,140
(Exit)

837
01:00:13,220 --> 01:00:14,500
Where is Lee Jong-tae?

838
01:00:17,060 --> 01:00:18,060
Well...

839
01:00:19,140 --> 01:00:20,460
Jong-tae, that punk.

840
01:00:21,060 --> 01:00:22,300
I can't reach him.

841
01:00:35,420 --> 01:00:36,420
I only see these two.

842
01:00:36,780 --> 01:00:37,820
There are three.

843
01:00:41,500 --> 01:00:43,060
(Slow Down, Slippery)

844
01:00:46,940 --> 01:00:47,940
The pills.

845
01:00:49,460 --> 01:00:51,180
In the trunk.

846
01:00:51,620 --> 01:00:53,020
Go ahead and cuff them.

847
01:01:06,100 --> 01:01:08,260
You jerks are dead meat now.

848
01:01:29,300 --> 01:01:30,300
What's that?

849
01:01:31,900 --> 01:01:33,220
A Glock. First time seeing one?

850
01:01:33,580 --> 01:01:35,660
Why do you even have that on you?

851
01:01:40,100 --> 01:01:41,980
(Exit)

852
01:01:44,420 --> 01:01:45,860
What are you doing?

853
01:01:46,500 --> 01:01:47,580
Just making sure he's dead.

854
01:01:49,540 --> 01:01:51,460
How could you kill a person
in front of a cop?

855
01:01:52,940 --> 01:01:54,980
Does this look like a human to you?

856
01:02:09,940 --> 01:02:11,300
Hands up!

857
01:02:12,140 --> 01:02:13,140
Hands up.

858
01:02:14,340 --> 01:02:15,540
It's over.

859
01:02:16,620 --> 01:02:18,780
Really? My goodness.

860
01:02:19,100 --> 01:02:21,620
Hey! How many shots did you fire?

861
01:02:21,980 --> 01:02:24,820
Thank goodness they were blanks.
You could be reprimanded for this.

862
01:02:26,940 --> 01:02:28,020
Did you do this?

863
01:02:28,220 --> 01:02:29,220
Stop!

864
01:02:31,980 --> 01:02:32,980
Please.

865
01:02:35,100 --> 01:02:36,940
Wait! Stop!

866
01:02:44,540 --> 01:02:47,220
When did he turn into that?

867
01:02:47,300 --> 01:02:48,620
I don't know!

868
01:02:52,340 --> 01:02:53,860
When I went to his place to get paid,

869
01:02:53,940 --> 01:02:56,420
he was already like that.
He had bitten his family to death.

870
01:02:56,540 --> 01:02:59,860
He was banging his head
on the bloody floor.

871
01:03:00,700 --> 01:03:02,140
Did he take Next?

872
01:03:02,220 --> 01:03:03,500
Yes, lots of it.

873
01:03:03,900 --> 01:03:05,780
He totally lost his mind
and ended up like that.

874
01:03:05,860 --> 01:03:07,500
And you used him like that?

875
01:03:09,900 --> 01:03:11,100
What else is he good for?

876
01:03:11,700 --> 01:03:14,500
He's the best guard dog
that doesn't need to be fed.

877
01:03:19,620 --> 01:03:21,300
You guys took the pills too, didn't you?

878
01:03:22,060 --> 01:03:23,260
You'll end up like him soon.

879
01:03:27,300 --> 01:03:28,700
-Get up, jerk.
-Yes.

880
01:03:31,180 --> 01:03:32,180
Okay.

881
01:03:32,700 --> 01:03:36,100
Mr. Jung.
There's a problem at the dormitory.

882
01:03:36,460 --> 01:03:37,460
What about it?

883
01:03:38,220 --> 01:03:39,660
Ms. Yoon is there now.

884
01:03:42,060 --> 01:03:44,100
What is she doing there?

885
01:04:05,820 --> 01:04:07,020
(They're not human.)

886
01:04:09,540 --> 01:04:10,540
What's not human?

887
01:04:11,860 --> 01:04:12,860
(All of them.)

888
01:04:35,540 --> 01:04:36,540
Quiet!

889
01:04:43,540 --> 01:04:44,540
Open this truck.

890
01:04:45,340 --> 01:04:46,340
Hurry!

891
01:04:49,780 --> 01:04:51,020
No, don't open it!

892
01:05:36,620 --> 01:05:41,460
=Happiness=

893
01:06:06,540 --> 01:06:07,700
(Be honest.)

894
01:06:08,900 --> 01:06:11,020
You think they're monsters.

895
01:06:11,460 --> 01:06:12,620
They want the case dropped.

896
01:06:13,140 --> 01:06:15,620
(The mad person disease is spreading
in the apartment complex.)

897
01:06:15,980 --> 01:06:18,180
(That pill causes
the mad person disease, doesn't it?)

898
01:06:19,140 --> 01:06:21,620
Bad rumors will only bring down
our property prices.

899
01:06:22,060 --> 01:06:23,260
(Block all of them in as planned.)

900
01:06:23,340 --> 01:06:25,580
(Lock them up
and just wait for them to die?)

901
01:06:25,740 --> 01:06:28,660
There was definitely something off
about the lady upstairs.

902
01:06:29,460 --> 01:06:30,740
(What is happening)

903
01:06:31,300 --> 01:06:32,900
(inside the apartment?)

